{"tid":460761,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[分享] 之前追我個男仔原來好有錢，好有上進心...","createTime":"2017-11-07T02:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T05:27:17.000Z","uid":82845,"like":4,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7c8bd886a8e4cf2c6dd2ac00ee39b997259607a9","tid":460761,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"之前有個男性朋友追我,我知佢由大學開始已經暗戀我一段時間<br />\n我單身後，佢開始約我單獨出街<br />\n<br />\n因為佢畢業後無耐自己走左去開一間鋪仔<br />\n我覺得佢職業寒酸，柒下柒下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n性格又孤寒，同我食飯連一蚊散子貼士都會攞返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我就冇表示，得閒先理下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢追左我大半年，我玩玩下佢，佢就再無下文<br />\n<br />\n但係最近我地圍內一個做地產的共同朋友話我知，<br />\n話個男仔剛剛買左層千幾萬的新樓，首期一下子比左600萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又查到佢已經供斷左層物業⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我計過佢月入應該有十多萬<br />\n而佢只係29歳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後對佢即刻改觀曬，而家好後悔當初冇理到佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">各位覺得我應唔應該主動搵返佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我咁樣會唔會好cheap?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係幾欣賞佢有上進心,可以買得起千幾萬樓,而唔係因為鍾意錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span>"},{"pid":"c257cfb625b3f7daaaf7585cab4a34cc1e3649a3","tid":460761,"uid":135910,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:45:12.000Z","msg":"死臭雞 見人發咗達先黐埋人哋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc47f7604f8142e9a46982bc245c7eb64102e36","tid":460761,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:45:15.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"674c0a512956b45db7172df45f768eac0d67efc2","tid":460761,"uid":151837,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"on9,又話欣賞人買得起層千幾萬既樓，又話唔係鐘意人啲錢<br />\n<br />\n咪又係貪人有樓，同鍾意人啲錢有咩分別呀<br />\n自己打自己嘴巴，唔好諗住打欣賞人地買到層樓咁撚好聽"},{"pid":"f48ad43c42ba7717f7b86c071a00e6bc3ca53ebd","tid":460761,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死臭雞 見人發咗達先黐埋人哋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4cc693936beef4e112efd20a9c0c187c35eb3e","tid":460761,"uid":53736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:48:28.000Z","msg":"鐘意上進心唔係鐘意錢 真係神來之筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae1764ac0f54463f9f91dae525314bc72221b88","tid":460761,"uid":151837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9,又話欣賞人買得起層千幾萬既樓，又話唔係鐘意人啲錢<br />\n<br />\n咪又係貪人有樓，同鍾意人啲錢有咩分別呀<br />\n自己打自己嘴巴，唔好諗住打欣賞人地買到層樓咁撚好聽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢買唔起層樓你會睇得上佢？<br />\n死臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab6b387ad541ca437ac86aad6e7d335c7cc040e","tid":460761,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9,又話欣賞人買得起層千幾萬既樓，又話唔係鐘意人啲錢<br />\n<br />\n咪又係貪人有樓，同鍾意人啲錢有咩分別呀<br />\n自己打自己嘴巴，唔好諗住打欣賞人地買到層樓咁撚好聽</blockquote><br />\n當初以為佢冇上進心,就咁就一世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9ac9a59cfea4d8f43c6d62d855237ce1d0f526","tid":460761,"uid":30089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"吔屎喇你, 唔係鐘意錢, 貪佢上進?<br />\n如果佢而家賣埋層樓, 將啲錢派撚晒街坊<br />\n叫你同佢由零再捱過, 你得閪咩, 咪撚玩喇五寶"},{"pid":"a191b9057e96ca33566948d6ece9905eebb7bd71","tid":460761,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"[呻下] 女朋友對波太細，好想偷食...<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/407543/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/407543/1?ref=android</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a39ad587aaecd8e3c693822586edf338e659f01","tid":460761,"uid":69348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:51:04.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好咁仆街啦"},{"pid":"3f67562783bd6eb02aebeeb323d787034a27e273","tid":460761,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"樓主唔係講到明分享咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6846176c1772476fed704caae86b65d1384db4","tid":460761,"uid":73089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"好明顯假膠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914e53a0b7f20af008b0b494e75d995c421e24d3","tid":460761,"uid":55550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/105922_b2f00980b48f27950422c84bf76aaf9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F105922_b2f00980b48f27950422c84bf76aaf9b.jpg&h=0284bee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697cb515e39a0a253ab78cbc66f26901c9e171eb","tid":460761,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"假膠"},{"pid":"6f17a15679f5a21da8586107ca389af5fbf02976","tid":460761,"uid":151837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0